---
// src/components/TecnicaBeneficios.astro
---

<section class="relative py-20  overflow-hidden  bg-gradient-to-b from-[#E5D1E7] to-white" id="nuestra-tecnica">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 -z-10">
    <div class="absolute top-10 left-0 w-72 h-72 bg-brand-purple/10 rounded-full blur-[100px] animate-pulse-slow"></div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-10 right-0 w-80 h-80 bg-brand-purple/5 rounded-full blur-[100px]"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-6xl">
    <div class="text-center ">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-brand-purple/5 backdrop-blur-md px-3 py-1 rounded-full border border-brand-purple/20 mb-6">
        <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-brand-purple rounded-full"></span>
        <span class="text-[10px] font-black text-brand-purple uppercase tracking-[0.2em]">Tecnología Brasileña</span>
      </div>

      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-black text-brand-dark mb-6 tracking-tighter">
        Nuestra <span class="text-brand-primary ">Técnica</span>
      </h1>

      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto relative">
        <div class="relative bg-white/60 backdrop-blur-xl rounded-[2.5rem] p-6 md:p-10 border border-brand-purple/10 shadow-[0_20px_50px_rgba(0,0,0,0.05)]">
          <p class="text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed text-slate-700 font-medium">
            <span class="text-brand-primary font-black ">Regenera la piel</span> desde el interior del organismo, mediante un dispositivo que utiliza 
            <span class="text-brand-dark font-bold underline decoration-brand-primary/30">microagujas de acero quirúrgico</span>, 
            que al hacer contacto provocan una ligera inflamación en la epidermis, estimulando la producción de 
            <span class="text-brand-dark font-bold">colágeno, elastina y ácido hialurónico</span>, 
            reduciendo la apariencia de las marcas hasta en un 
            <span class="relative inline-block ml-1">
              <span class="relative z-10 font-black text-3xl md:text-4xl text-brand-primary italic">95%</span>
              <span class="absolute bottom-1 left-0 w-full h-3 bg-brand-primary/20 -z-10"></span>
            </span>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="relative py-12 " id="beneficios">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-6xl">
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-end justify-between mb-10 gap-4">
      <div class="text-center md:text-left">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black text-brand-dark uppercase tracking-tight">
          Beneficios <span class="text-brand-primary ">Exclusivos</span>
        </h2>
        <div class="w-20 h-1.5 bg-brand-primary rounded-full mt-2 mx-auto md:mx-0"></div>
      </div>
      <p class="text-slate-500 max-w-xs text-sm font-medium leading-tight text-center md:text-right">
        Ciencia aplicada al rejuvenecimiento celular permanente.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-4 md:gap-6">
      <article class="group relative bg-white p-7 rounded-[2rem] border border-slate-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-500 hover:-translate-y-1">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-brand-purple/5 text-brand-primary rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5 group-hover:bg-brand-primary group-hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300">
          <svg class="w-7 h-7" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-black text-brand-dark mb-2">Cicatrices y Estrías</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">
          Elimina marcas, cicatrices atróficas, hipertróficas, queloides y secuelas de acné con resultados visibles.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="group relative bg-white p-7 rounded-[2rem] border border-slate-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-500 hover:-translate-y-1">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-brand-purple/5 text-brand-primary rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5 group-hover:bg-brand-primary group-hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300">
          <svg class="w-7 h-7" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path d="M14.828 14.828a4 4 0 01-5.656 0M9 10h.01M15 10h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-black text-brand-dark mb-2">Textura Uniforme</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">
          Piel suave y radiante, poros minimizados y acabado perfecto desde la primera sesión.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="group relative bg-white p-7 rounded-[2rem] border border-slate-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-500 hover:-translate-y-1">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-brand-purple/5 text-brand-primary rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5 group-hover:bg-brand-primary group-hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300">
          <svg class="w-7 h-7" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-black text-brand-dark mb-2">Sin Cirugía</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">
          Procedimiento ambulatorio, mínimamente invasivo con resultados superiores al bótox.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="group relative bg-white p-7 rounded-[2rem] border border-slate-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-500 hover:-translate-y-1">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-brand-purple/5 text-brand-primary rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5 group-hover:bg-brand-primary group-hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300">
          <svg class="w-7 h-7" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-black text-brand-dark mb-2">Resultados Permanentes</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">
          Resultados visibles y duraderos sin depender de activos externos ni reaplicaciones.
        </p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>



<style>
  .animate-pulse-slow {
    animation: pulse 6s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.6, 1) infinite;
  }
  @keyframes pulse {
    0%, 100% { opacity: 0.1; }
    50% { opacity: 0.3; }
  }
</style>